                                       QueryRequestBuilder params)

        Query HP Haven OnDemand for documents matching query text using a token proxy provided by a TokenProxyService
        Parameters:
        text - The query text
        params - Additional parameters to be sent as part of the request
        Returns:
        A list of documents that match the query text
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - If a TokenProxyService has not been defined

      • queryTextIndexWithReference

        QueryResults<T> queryTextIndexWithReference(String reference,
                                            QueryRequestBuilder params)
                                     throws HodErrorException
        Query HP Haven OnDemand for documents using query text from an object store object using a token proxy provided by a TokenProxyService
        Parameters:
        reference - An HP Haven OnDemand reference obtained from either the Expand Container or Store Object API. The contents of the object will be used as the query text
        params - Additional parameters to be sent as part of the request
        Returns:
        A list of documents that match the query text
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - If a TokenProxyService has not been defined
        HodAuthenticationFailedException - If the token associated with the token proxy has expired
        HodErrorException
